7511-102419-0001 BUT I'VE A CHANCE TO DAY SO I WILL NOT LET IT PASS UNUSED WE ARE IN THE LAST CAMP RIGHT ON THE HUNTING GROUND IN THE MIDST OF THE FRAY WE HAVE SAID GOOD BYE TO DEAR ELIZABETH AND I MUST TELL YOU ABOUT HER BECAUSE SHE REALLY COMES FIRST
